n face detection. With this approach, however, no significantly\nincreased human-likeness was found. Possible applications of overt visual\nattention in DCNNs and further implications for theories of face detection are\ndiscussed.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 21 Jun 2022 17:59:23 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 6 Sep 2022 16:45:41 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-09-07"}
