ic Kerr-Sen-AdS black hole and its ultraspinning counterpart to\nthose of the dyonic Kerr-Newman-AdS black hole and the ultraspinning\ncounterpart. Depending on the dyonic charge parameters, it is found that\nextremal ultraspinning dyonic Kerr-Sen-AdS black hole is not always\nsuperentropic.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 22 Jun 2022 06:29:41 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sat, 12 Nov 2022 03:37:09 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-11-15"}
