ome cases. The interactivity of the map facilitated\ninterpretation. This study was small in scope, but it provides one piece of\nknowledge about the information needs related to algorithmic classifications.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 22 Jun 2022 07:41:02 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-06-23"}
