allenging while $t_c$ and $t^*$ can be directly readout by\nmeasuring the spin polarizations of four Dirac points and the time-dependent\nparticle density, respectively. Our work reveals the novel interacting effects\non the topological phases and shall promote the experimental observation.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 22 Jun 2022 12:37:15 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 4 Jul 2022 04:08:49 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Fri, 12 Aug 2022 03:45:36 GMT"},{"version":"v4","created":"Wed, 8 Mar 2023 03:45:38 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-03-29"}
