ove measurability of this map for each topology. Under stronger\nregularity assumptions, we show continuity on explicit compact subsets of the\nproduct topology (1). We relate these results to the expected signature model\nof [15].\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 22 Jun 2022 14:57:50 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 29 Jun 2022 16:34:22 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-06-30"}
